column2: Pact.Rd <- ggplot(Pact, aes(x=Date, y = Rdark.mean, group = Treatment, color = Treatment)) +
xlab("Date") + theme(axis.text.x=element_text(angle=60, hjust=1)) + # x-axis label and rotating text on x axis
ylab("Respiration Rate ([umol/cm2/hr])") + ylim(c(0, 0.8)) + # y-axis label and y axis range
